What you need to know:

With the latest reports of Reysol accepting the six-million Euros bid, Al-Duhail is now free to open talks with the centre-forward who had recently extended his contract with Kashiwa to January 31, 2023If Olunga and Al-Duhail agree terms and he joins the side, he will be the second high profile player to play in Qatar’s topflight league after Dennis ‘The Menace’ Oliech